Michael Duvert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Duvert 0 Michael Duvert is an American actor who plays Dax Ryston on the MyNetworkTV limited-run serial Saints Sinners. He previously appeared on the daytime drama One Life to Live and on All My Children in 1994. Michael_Duvert is an_American_actor who plays Dax_Ryston on the_MyNetworkTV_limited-run_serial_Saints_ . He previously appeared on the_daytime_drama One_Life to_Live and on All_My_Children in 1994 .
